parameters: \n<Momo>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Good evening~!
\n<Hat Man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Whoa!? W-What is it?!
\n<Momo>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Ready, aim, fire~! \I[12]

\n<Momo>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Both of you, say it according to the
meeting!

\n<Sawa>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]I'm sorry... I hesitated at the last
moment...
\n<Kino>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Hmm... Ah, sorry.

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]What the hell are you guys doing, entering
without permission--... Oh? Oh my?

\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]The brown-haired person's expression
softened as soon as they saw Kino.

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Kino-chan~♪ What's up? Are you here to spoil me
again?
\n<Hat Man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Huh? Could it be, from the other day?

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Hey, Udo-san brought a girl for us to share.
We had a threesome until morning
(laughs).

\n<Man with a Hat>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Damn it, it's always when I'm not around...
And she's pretty cute too... Huh? I feel
like I've seen her somewhere before...

\n<Sawa>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Kino... Could it be that you were familiar with
this place?

\n<Kino>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Ah... Please keep it a secret from those two.
This is the condition for me helping
out.
\n<Momo>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Kino-chan...

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]What... Could it be, today you'll entertain the
three of us?

\n<Kino>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]That's right~☆ I couldn't forget about what
happened with you guys~ so I came back
again♪

\n<Man with a Hat>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Shaa! Kino-chan is mine to use, you know!
She's totally my type♪

\n<Momo>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Well then... Momo wants big brother to do it
with her~ \I[12]

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Hey, good job♪ How about bringing that girl
along too?

\n<Hat Man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Huh? You've had your fun enough! Leave this
one to me!

\n<Brown-haired man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Who cares! It's your fault for not being
here!

\n<Sawa>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[FF]Well then... I wonder if I should join in
with the one who makes them cum first♪
\n<Brown-haired man & Hat-wearing man>\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]We definitely won't lose, \}!

\F[67]\FF[99]\AA[F]Kino is helping us even though it's
unpleasant for her. I know she's not a
character, but it would be disrespectful
to her if we were embarrassed here.

Two pairs of men and women press their
bodies together, burying their faces in
each other's crotches to comfort each
other, while I move to the blind spot of
the men.

\n<Sawa>(...Thanks to Kino and the others for skillfully
guiding the men. Just wait, I'll finish
it quickly...)

I take out a small spray bottle that I
had hidden in the pocket of my jacket.

\n<Sawa>(I never thought that what Udo Director
gave me would actually be useful...)

...It was a suspicious sleep spray that was
not for sale. I used it when I went to
\N[5]'s room on the second night of the
training camp to make him fall asleep.

First, I approach Kino and the others. The man
wearing a hat is completely absorbed in
Kino's crotch and doesn't notice my
approach at all.

\n<Man with a Hat>Slurp, chu, chuba, fusu... fufusu... Hm?
Huh...? Ahh... Zzz...

Kino stands up and heads towards Momo before
I can even stand up, gently supporting
the head of the man who has fallen
asleep and placing it on the floor.
\n<Sawa>...Kino?

\n<Brown-haired man>Haa, haa, Momo-chan\I[12] Momo-chan, I can't
hold back anymore...
\n<Kino>Hey, premature ejaculation guy.

\n<Brown-haired man>Huh? Kino-chan? What, you still longing for
my dick... ----ugh!?

Kino placed their foot on the face of the
man they were looking up at... and then
boldly stepped on it.
\n<Brown-haired man>Ngoh... Y-you...
\n<Momo>Mmmph!? N-Nnh...

I hurriedly approached the man and
sprayed his face with a spray.

\n<Brown-haired man>Huh? Fuwa... Huh... What's this...
Nyannra... Nn... Ah... Zzz...

\n<Kino>Heh... This guy got his head stepped on and
ejaculated.

\n<Sawa>Geez... You got a little flustered, didn't
you...

\n<Kino>Sorry, sorry... but this guy's smug face is
really pissing me off...

\n<Momo>Cough, cough... Ugh... It's stuck in the back
of my throat...

...Suddenly, the air was filled with a sense of
relief.

\n<Sawa>\F[66]...With this, they shouldn't wake up for a few
hours. Let's meet up with \N[5]-san and
the others.

\n<Momo>\F[66]\FF[92]\AA[FF]By the way, it went well, didn't it? They
were completely off guard.

\n<Sawa>\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[F]That... might be thanks to Kino. If Udo-san had
received a confirmation call, it could
have been dangerous...

\n<Kino>\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[FF]For Sawa, that was just a coincidence...
What were you planning to do if these
guys tried to contact us?

\n<Sawa>\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[F]Well... at that time, I was thinking of hugging
them, maybe even taking off their
clothes forcefully and leading them to
'that'...

\n<Momo>\F[66]\FF[92]\AA[FF]My perspective on Sawa has changed after
this incident...

\n<Kino>\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[FF]The ones who seem quiet are actually the
scariest. But personally, I have a good
impression of them.

\n<Sawa>\F[66]\FF[91]\AA[F]I was just desperate... A-anyway, put on
some clothes! Once you've taken their
phones, hurry back!

And so... we successfully cut off the means
of communication to the town, leaving
the sleeping men behind and leaving the
cabin behind...
